'''布洛阿特峰'''（{{lang-en|Broad Peak}}；{{lang-ur|بروڈ پیک|brod pack}}，為英文名的音譯；{{bo|z=ཕལྕན་ཀངྲི་|p=|w=phalcan kangri}}，為英文名的意譯<ref name=evnews>{{cite web | url=http://www.everestnews.com/stories024/bphistory.htm| title=Broad Peak: Some background and History | publisher=Everest News | access-date = 2014-01-26}}</ref>）位于[[中華人民共和國|中国]]和[[巴控克什米尔|巴控克什米尔]]边境的[[喀喇昆仑山脉|喀喇昆仑山脉]]，距离[[乔戈里峰|乔戈里峰]]约8公里，海拔8,051公尺，是世界第十二高峰。山名音譯自英國探險家{{le|馬丁·康威|Martin Conway, 1st Baron Conway of Allington}}於1892年所稱的「Broad Peak」，即「寬闊的山峰」<ref>Richard Sale and John Cleare, ''Climbing the World's 14 Highest Mountains: The History of the 8, 000-Meter Peaks'', The Mountaineers, 2000</ref>，指布洛阿特峰寬達1.5公里的峰頂<ref name=peakware>{{cite web|work=Pearware.com|title=Broad Peak|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303235523/http://www.peakware.com/peaks.html?pk=389|url=http://www.peakware.com/peaks.html?pk=389|dead-url=yes|archivedate=2016-03-04|accessdate=2014-01-26}}</ref>。

